@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.36)
    v1 = v2
    v0 = 0.67
    v0 = v0
    v1 = 0.62
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.46)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
